channel.title: Object deleting problems
channel.description:
Hey guys, I am trying to delete objects... i know how to do it, it's just trees seem like a royal pain in the ass.
Trees seem to be between two tiles/squares. and they are not particularly on any 1 coordinate...
I was just wondering how i delete trees... do i add two sets of coordinates when i delete trees.
Help would be appreciated.
Thanks ~ Ziege Terra ~

item.title: Object deleting problems
item.dc:creator: @koopa_king koopa king
item.description:
@koopa_king wrote:

Normally you can right click the object and it will show you what coordinate it is on. If it takes up two coordinates, put them both under “deletethatobject”.
